---
title: Hearty Bacon and Lentil Mushroom Cottage Pie with Cheesy Mash Top and Peas
description: A British favourite, cottage pie is most recognisable as a deeply savoury layer of meat filling topped with mash, but here we're making it vegetarian with lentils and mushrooms for a filling and wholesome meal. Best enjoyed after baking until golden and scrumptious!
